minor mappillai ( tamil : &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ) is a 1996 tamil comedy film directed by v. c. &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; starring ajith kumar and ranjith in the leading roles . the pair play small-time crooks who hook up with a rags-to-riches businessman , played by vadivelu , to take revenge on a millionaire , played by srividya . the film also featured newcomers rajkumar , subhashree , keerthana and bharathi , while vivek appeared in a supporting role . it was released on 28 june 1996 .